{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_10_level_st_10-04","storyGroup":"main_10","storySort":88,"storyDependence":"main_10_level_st_10-04","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"10-19","storyName":"远方星火","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在一所位于乌萨斯北部小城的大学校园内，塔露拉找到了她一直在找的“人”。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_st_10-04","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"st_10-04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":26,"characters":["塔露拉","乌萨斯青年学生","骏鹰老师","整合运动战士","九","整合运动术师","卡谢娜","？？？","阿赫茉妮","风笛","陈"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"st04","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_school.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“......下面，请同学们翻到课本第一百三十二页。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"泰拉历31年，骏鹰帝国正式更名为乌萨斯帝国。这段历史我们已经花了两堂课来分析和探讨。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"学界普遍认为，骏鹰失去君主的资格，其源头在于统治阶层的腐朽与无能，以及代表了社会主要生产力的乌萨斯的崛起。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这场战争被描述为乌萨斯的起义，代表了先民对神民权力的挑战。自此，神民在泰拉诸国都逐渐丧失了盘踞统治地位的正当性。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"然而，当我们换个角度去回顾这场战争，很容易就会产生一系列疑问。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在当时的社会情境下，如果占据统治地位的并非骏鹰，而是另一支乌萨斯，变革是否还会发生？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","text":"如果身为统治者的骏鹰，并未坚持种族差异政策，不再侵占乌萨斯的财产，给予乌萨斯同等的升迁机会......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"骏鹰帝国的覆灭是否就能被避免，还是来得更早？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","text":"如果......当年可汗的骑兵并未踏足这片土地呢？”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":17},{"type":"subtitle","id":18},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","fadetime":"1.5","id":21},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯青年学生","text":"你好，你也是来听卡谢娜老师上课的吗？","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"卡谢娜......老师？","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯青年学生","text":"是啊，由她负责授课的乌萨斯帝国史一直很受欢迎。","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯青年学生","text":"最近总能看到像你一样的年轻人在走廊旁听。你不是我们学校的学生，对吧？你看起来不像个大学生。","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯青年学生","text":"其实你可以走进去的，卡谢娜老师不介意你们站在教室后面。这样你会听得更清楚些。","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不必了。她的声音我已经听得足够清楚。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌萨斯青年学生","text":"那好吧，反正这堂课也快结束了。我还有其他课要上，我先走啦。","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"请快些离开这里吧。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":38},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":39},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":40},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“这些问题的答案，你们或许并不能在任何课本上找到。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":41},{"type":"subtitle","text":"但我希望你们好好想一想。在吃饭的时候，洗澡的时候，甚至睡觉的时候......让问题回荡在自己的大脑里。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":42},{"type":"subtitle","text":"当一个念头徘徊得足够久，就将它写下来。我乐于看见你们的观点。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":43},{"type":"subtitle","text":"好了，这堂课该结束了。在下一次铃声响起之前，享受你们短暂的自由吧。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":44},{"type":"subtitle","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":48},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"骏鹰老师","text":"你有什么疑问吗，同学？","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我找到你了。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":56},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":57},{"type":"character","id":58},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":59},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","fadetime":"1.5","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"她为什么要进城去？","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"为了找一个人。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"什么人值得我们冒这个险？","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"九，明明是你说的，我们在乌萨斯的所有行动都不能靠近移动城市。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"——","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"我们不是一直都想审判她吗？在她开口之前，她还需要找一个答案。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"如果没有这个答案，她自己都无法相信自己吐露的字句。那样的话，我们更无法相信她。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"我们本来就不该相信她！","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"她一个人进了城，万一就这样一走了之呢？我们之前为了救出她而做的一切努力，我们之后关于她的全部计划，都会付之一炬！","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......不会的。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"因为她自己清楚，她已经无处可去。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"而且，只要你们还信我，我就会向你们保证，无论她去了哪里，我都能再次把她抓出来。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"我相信你......但这是基于你这一年多里带着我们做的所有事情。","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"你和她不一样，你没那么喜欢耍嘴皮子。九，这是我们都很喜欢你的一点。你最好不要把这个好习惯给弄丢了。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你担心我会被她影响？","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"那还真有点困难。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_332_1$1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"九，有纠察队靠近——","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_332_1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"注意隐蔽。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"和我们预计的一样。再过半个小时，这条路线就会不再安全。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......她最好能及时回来。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"character","id":94},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_school.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":95},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","id":96},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"骏鹰老师","text":"我还以为能更早见到你——","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"骏鹰老师","text":"——塔露拉。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......卡谢娜。这名字还是这么直白浅显啊，科西切。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#2$1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"啊......名字。名字只是一个称谓，假如你嫌这些音节会勾起一些不快的回忆，你也可以叫我菲奥莉特。","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"算了，你叫什么我都不关心。你的名字，就如同你的皮囊一样，没有让我记住的价值。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那你是为何而来呢，塔露拉？","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你是想从我嘴里得到一个确切的答案吗？你想听见我告诉你，是的，科西切已经离开了你，如今的你只是塔露拉？","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那你会得到你想要的。我现在就可以这么说，就如你希望听见的那样，一字不差。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"问题是——你愿意相信吗？","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你想让我相信一条黑蛇？","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这是你的新把戏吗，科西切？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你给了我足够多的信息，好让我在最短的时间内找到你——我只能认为，你是有意诱使我来到这里。","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那么，你回去看过了？回到我们共同的家？","id":117,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那不是我的家。那只是阴谋的发源地，毒蛇们喜爱的老巢。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你的说法真令我伤心啊。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"但你还是读了我的信件，不是吗？你始终记得科西切公爵用来接收蛇鳞密信的渠道。那些占了公爵领的秘密警察就找不到。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——一封十年前就已寄出的信，寄信人就在这所学校。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我都不知该赞叹你的深谋远虑，还是该庆幸那条渠道的确封存了十年，你的蛇鳞们早已朽作尘埃。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"领地的荒废令你感到高兴吗？塔露拉，他们本来能在你的治理下获得更好的生活，而不是被第四集团军撕扯得不成模样。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"别装作你比我更关心他们了。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"说吧，是什么让你甘愿待在这最北边的小城里？","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"科西切，我记得你更喜欢靠南一些的城市。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不仅因为那里的空气更加湿润，还因为培育了一代又一代权力核心的土壤也更适合你的阴谋滋长。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"冻原——冻原就不同了。这里的人们过得更苦，光是对粮食收成的担忧就足以占满他们的大脑。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你引以为豪的演说，于他们而言就像佩在你身上的假花一样，徒有其表，毫无用处。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#6$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"塔露拉......塔露拉。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"如果我说，我在这里，是因为这附近的冻原上有你留下的足迹呢？","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那我会说你胡说八道。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"“人类的历史，就是斗争史。”","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你明明都记得的。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那些年里，我教会你的一切，你都用在了你后来的抗争上。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"既然你都记得，那么冻原上的感染者斗士塔露拉，和继承了公爵之位的塔露拉，对我来说又有多大分别？","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可你毁掉了我在冻原上建立起的一切。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#4$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"是我毁掉的吗？","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"在你心里，犯下这一系列致命错误的，究竟是谁？","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#2$1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"倘若你真认同自己无罪，你根本没有必要用一年半的时间去思考自己该选择何种方式的死亡。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你会转头就投入下一场轰轰烈烈的抗争中。","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"塔露拉，我知道你为什么要来到我面前。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你想要用对我的审判来审判你自己，你想听见我的忏悔从而开始你的忏悔。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你要的——不过是一点可怜的心理安慰。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......说下去。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#6$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你让我说下去？我还以为——","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你以为我会让你看见我的怒火？不，科西切，你还不配。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"到目前为止，你说的每一句话，都曾在我的脑海中预演过。一年半并不是一段很短的时间，而被关在罗德岛上的我确实无事可做。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"想从我手中活下去，你还需要说一些更新鲜的。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"好吧，看得出来，那段自我监禁的时光让你变得更有耐心了。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"但我提起冻原，并不是为了刺痛你。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"塔露拉......看看这所学校吧。看看那些学生脸上的神采。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"他们相信五月的阳光会融化冻原上的冰雪，也相信着比冻原还硬的乌萨斯会在他们脚下改变。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"而你又想用你那些龌龊的思想，去玷污他们的天真？","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你以为我是想在他们之中寻找下一个继承人？","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"不，塔露拉，我只是一名普普通通的大学老师而已。我传递的只有知识和思想，并没有任何权力或者财富握在我的手里。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"假如他们想要权力，他们可以自己用双手去争取。假如他们渴望阴谋，他们同样能从我传授的知识里找到最合适的技巧。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你是想让我相信——你在我身上遭遇的失败，竟然让你一蹶不振、秉性大改？","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#9$1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"失败？我从来不认为那是失败。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"整合运动并没有彻底毁在切尔诺伯格核心城，科西切的计划也一样。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"是的，你们暂时阻止了科西切，他没能等来他想要的那场足以立刻改变乌萨斯的战争。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"但乌萨斯还是步上了科西切为她设定的轨道。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"战争正在发生。议会和军队的摩擦依然升级了，人们的意志也在一场又一场冲突中碰撞出新的火花。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"而我，我会站在最富有活力的土壤上，尽我所能地播撒种子。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"我将引导......或者说促成这些变革的发生。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我记得你向我否认过教育大众的意义。","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"当事态发生了变化，一位统治者却依旧按照过去的方法行事，那他必然会走向毁灭。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你依然......以统治者自居。我明白了，你其实一点都没有改变。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"差点忘了，你痛恨这个词语，就跟你厌恨科西切的控制一样。我早就告诉过你，我并不在乎谁来统治。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"自从乌萨斯从骏鹰手中夺下这片土地，权力的更迭在明里暗中发生过多少次？","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"塔露拉，你就是我，我也是你。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"我们想要的，都是乌萨斯仍能在我们掌心迸出星火。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#8$1","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"这场火......早晚会点燃整个乌萨斯。不，不仅乌萨斯。维多利亚......还有其他国家，都会被卷进来。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"大火过后，这片土地会变得更加繁荣，还是迎来毁灭？","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"乌萨斯走过了自己的第一个千年——而我会令它走向第二个，第三个。这才是黑蛇存在的意义。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"黑蛇不死，不是因为我有着自我存续的意志，而是因为乌萨斯必须活下去。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"4","id":206},{"type":"dialog","id":207},{"type":"character","id":208},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_bg_bg_manorindoor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":210},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$tense_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_tense_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":212,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_236","fadetime":"3","id":213},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"阿斯兰的王嗣已经回到了伦蒂尼姆？","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"看样子是的。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"这是萨卡兹有意赠送给我们的消息，作为我们先前送回那几名萨卡兹信使的回报。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_236","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"回报？","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"他们不过是希望借我们的手，让公爵之间的争斗进一步升级。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"显而易见。但从他们的做法中，我们也能看出来，伦蒂尼姆城内的局势又起了变化，萨卡兹有些着急。","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_236","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"萨卡兹还说了什么吗？","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#7","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"没什么有用的了。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#5","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"啧，自从“间谍”暴露，我们能收到的伦蒂尼姆的消息变少了。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_236","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可惜。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#2","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"是啊......真可惜。好在我们的损失还在可控范围内。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"对了，还有另一条可能很重要的消息。","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"这条消息是一位与我们合作的哥伦比亚军火商透露的——","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"一个月前，那支名为整合运动的队伍迎回了他们之前的“领袖”。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_236","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你是说......","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_236.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"塔露拉。","id":241,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8e/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_228_1#6","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿赫茉妮","text":"要是之前的情报全部属实的话，她......她很有可能也是德拉克呀。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_avg_npc_228_1-6.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":244},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"character","id":247},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","fadetime":"1.5","id":250},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":251},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":252,"musicid":2},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"真、真的吗？你你你没骗我？！","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......我骗你这个干什么？","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#7","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"打我一拳吧。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f6/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你犯什么傻？","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#3","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"你快打我一拳，不然我真的以为自己是在做梦！","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"要不然你撞个墙试试？不过，不要花太大力气，撞破了别人家墙壁的话，你还得花时间跟这个郡的骑警解释。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_char_010_chen_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"我......我一时间都不知道该说什么......","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#3","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你真这么惊讶？天天念叨着队长肯定没死的人明明是你。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ab/Avg_char_010_chen_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"可我还以为......还以为......","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"以为她还在哪里等着你去救她？","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#4","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"嗯。","id":273,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"但是知道队长逃出来了，果然还是更加惊喜啊！","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"谢谢你，陈陈，没有你，我就不可能认识罗德岛的人，我没有加入罗德岛，他们也不会帮我救出队长，太好了，呜呜呜......","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-8.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"character","id":278},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.7","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":280},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#2","id":281},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......别抱上来！","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/16/Avg_char_010_chen_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"呜呜，可是我好高兴！","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-8.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#6","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"至少......别那么大力气......呃唔......","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_char_010_chen_6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":288},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#2","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"等一下，陈陈，那......那你是不是就要走了？你答应了要帮我救队长，而现在队长已经不需要我去救了......","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这种时候，你的脑子倒是转得挺快。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"实话说，我不是没想过。在得知她逃出了罗德岛以后，我一直在考虑去找她。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_222_bpipe_1#8","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"风笛","text":"其实，我能看出来的......","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_222_bpipe_1-8.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但陈晖洁从来不是半途而废的人。","id":297,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"走了这么久，我们好不容易得到了一些线索。","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"风笛，我会帮你继续追查下去。“等到鬼魂部队重新暴露在阳光下的那一天”——我会去做我早就该做的事。","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我会去找塔露拉。","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_char_010_chen_1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":301},{"type":"dialog","id":302},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"character","id":304},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_school.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":307},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":309},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":310,"musicid":3},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"塔露拉，用上科西切教会你的所有技巧，看一看吧，看看我说的这些话是不是都发自真心。","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不必了。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那你还想着在这里杀死我吗？为了躲开城内卫兵的视线，你没有拿剑。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你只能用你的火焰处死我。你是想在这些喜爱着我的学生面前......犯下这样恐怖的罪行吗？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"想要杀死你，我还不至于会惊动别人。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"别忘了，科西切，这也是你教会我的知识。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"杀死我......就能令你满意吗？","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"假如你并不能感到满足，我还能给你第二个名字，甚至第三个。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#5$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......你是想告诉我，在乌萨斯境内的黑蛇，还不止你一个。","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#2$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你也能当作是我为了活下去而设法欺骗你。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/61/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#2$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":328},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":329},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":330},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-100","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":332},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#2$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你的新躯体......很脆弱。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"杀死你，并不比杀死那个老斐迪亚要难。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那你还等什么？快，让我的躯体化作灰烬......洒满这昏暗的走廊！","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"“恐怖的感染者刽子手再现大学校园”——这会是第二天的报纸头条。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"你......不会在意这些恶名。","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"顺带一提，我也不怕三分钟之后就会赶到这里的纠察队。","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"但是......你那些守在城外的新老朋友......他们还不是皇帝内卫的对手。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"即便他们在一些掌权者的授意下，暂且容忍你回到乌萨斯......也绝对不会允许你在乌萨斯境内杀人。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......科西切。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你觉得，要是内卫们知道不死的怪物——切尔诺伯格事件的主谋就在这里，比起抓住我，他们会不会先把视线和刀刃一起投向你？","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_415_1#7$1","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"......","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡谢娜","text":"那么，你为何还不动手？","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_415_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":353},{"type":"dialog","id":354},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":355},{"type":"character","id":356},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":358},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"......时间快到了。","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"她还没回来？九，你是不是看错她了？","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"万一到了约定时间，她真的没有出现，你们就按原计划撤退。","id":365,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_016","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动战士","text":"你呢？","id":367,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_016.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"她还戴着我的镣铐，那她就是我的犯人。我会亲手把她捉拿归案。","id":369,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":370},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":371,"musicid":4},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......那你可以省点力气了。","id":372},{"type":"dialog","id":373},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":374},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","fadetime":"1.5","id":375},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"——塔露拉。","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你回来了，而且一分钟都没有迟到。你见完你要见的人了？","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"差不多。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"所以呢？","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你不会是想让我谈谈收获吧？我本来不打算让那些又臭又长的絮叨污染你的耳朵。","id":385,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"不错，你精神了不少，都会开玩笑了。","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"那个恶神呢？你成功杀死他了吗？","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她说她不再是那个人了。","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你相信？","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我不信。但我也不再是那个以为杀了她就能解决问题的塔露拉。","id":394,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我不会允许她离开我的视线。有必要的时候，我会立刻动手。","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可我总有一种预感......","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"预感？","id":398,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不死的恶神......终将死去。可杀死她的，不会是我。","id":400,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——乌萨斯会杀死她。","id":401,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"她至今仍以为自己能操弄人们的意志，而我们会证明给她看——","id":402,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"终有一天，觉醒的人们会将愚昧的统治者狠狠地抛下。","id":403,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在那之后，乌萨斯将再无黑蛇。","id":404,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"那现在呢？","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"2","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"现在，在最终回到这里之前，我们先去一趟维多利亚。","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_043_1#2","name2":"char_011_talula_1#3","focus":"1","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"九","text":"你终于决定与我们同行了？","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_043_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_011_talula_1#3","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我是你的囚犯，除了跟着你们，我无处可去。","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"而且是你说的......那里的感染者，正在等我们。","id":413,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_char_011_talula_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":414},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":417},{"type":"character","id":418},{"type":"image","id":419}],"characters":["塔露拉","乌萨斯青年学生","骏鹰老师","整合运动战士","九","整合运动术师","卡谢娜","？？？","阿赫茉妮","风笛","陈"]}